tecting pipeline\n.dev/releases/backlog/v3.1_unified-audit-gating-v1.2.1/proposals/spec-refactor-plan.md:111:gate, spec transition) and are normative additions to the release scope.\n.dev/releases/backlog/v3.1_unified-audit-gating-v1.2.1/proposals/spec-refactor-plan.md:155:>   EXEMPT (excluded from SilentSuccessDetector signal denominators) per §5.2 normative rule\n.dev/releases/backlog/v3.1_unified-audit-gating-v1.2.1/proposals/spec-refactor-plan.md:181:[Omitted long matching line]\n...\n</persisted-output>"}]},"uuid":"cceb2838-6bf5-4346-a1c8-53f16b0e2b8e","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:48:33.630Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"66faa586-cb18-4d90-b88d-886395f0d1c6","userType":"external","cwd":"/config/workspace/IronClaude","sessionId":"caf57f20-b6f0-47d7-a404-b3840c9c44e5","version":"2.1.77","gitBranch":"v3.0-AuditGates","slug":"bright-juggling-reef"}
